definition: to herd/to breed livestock/to govern (old)/government official (old)

pinyin: Su1 ge2 lan2 mu4 yang2 quan3

sentences.english: The pup looked to be a cross between a Lab and a German shepherd.
sentences.chinese: 看起來是拉布拉多獵犬和德國牧羊犬交配的品種。

sentences.english: These herding dogs help move and protect the animals.
sentences.chinese: 這些牧羊犬可以驅趕並保護這些牲畜。

sentences.english: With the help of two dogs, he drove the sheep down the mountain.
sentences.chinese: 在兩隻牧羊犬的幫助下，他把羊從山上趕了下來。

sentences.english: Even the family's collie was bitten.
sentences.chinese: 她甚至咬家裏的牧羊犬。

sentences.english: When does a sheepdog become a sheepdog?
sentences.chinese: 牧羊犬何時才能成爲真正的牧羊犬？

sentences.english: When does a sheepdog become a sheepdog?
sentences.chinese: 牧羊犬何時才能成爲真正的牧羊犬？

sentences.english: If you get any shaggier. you'll look like a sheepdog.
sentences.chinese: 你頭髮亂七八糟的看起來像個牧羊犬。

sentences.english: It said that number one fifty-three was a mixed Shepherd, six months old.
sentences.chinese: 上面說153號是隻混種牧羊犬，6個月大。

sentences.english: The trotting gait of the Shetland Sheepdog should denote effortless speed and smoothness.
sentences.chinese: 喜樂蒂牧羊犬的小跑步態顯得輕鬆而順暢。

sentences.english: Now this black-and-white Border collie, age seven, knows more than 1, 000 words.
sentences.chinese: 這隻七歲的黑白博德牧羊犬，認得超過千字。

sentences.english: "Papa, " I said, "I don't want an old collie dog.
sentences.chinese: “爸爸，”我說，“我不想要一隻老牧羊犬。

sentences.english: Bitzer is the Farmer's faithful sheepdog and also good friend to Shaun.
sentences.chinese: 比澤爾是農夫的忠實牧羊犬，也是肖恩的好兄弟。

sentences.english: The merle colours were very common in the early days of the breed.
sentences.chinese: 在早期的邊境牧羊犬中，山鳥色曾經非常普遍。

sentences.english: Border Collies have traditionally been bred solely for working ability.
sentences.chinese: 邊境牧羊犬一直以來單純爲了牧羊繁殖下來的。

sentences.english: The younger blind dog was a collie with congenital blindness.
sentences.chinese: 年輕的失明的寵物狗爲先天性失明的柯利牧羊犬。

sentences.english: Like sheep without any need for a sheepdog, we keep each other in line.
sentences.chinese: 我們彼此一致，就像無需牧羊犬看守的羊羣。
